-!- FUNCTION: Activates, in anaerobic conditions, the transcription of
    the fermentative operons lctEP and alsDS, of the hmp gene encoding
    a flavohemoglobin-like protein, the nitrite reductase operon nasDE
    and the heme biosynthesis genes hemN and hemZ.
-!- INDUCTION: By fnr. Autorepressed.
